{"tid":2456495,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"警方流動攝錄隊打擊違例泊車等行為","createTime":"2021-03-22T03:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T13:38:03.000Z","uid":342595,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"92ff749ff886c2159ae0220fe79e353253f8f093","tid":2456495,"uid":342595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方派出流動攝錄隊，在全港打擊違例泊車等違例行為。<br />\n<br />\n手持攝錄機的警員，在警車拍攝街上違例泊車的情況，但不會即場發告票，警方會稍後再向涉事司機發出告票。警方指流動攝錄隊，自2019年第二季起執法，該年度發出約5000張定額罰款告票。去年再增加人手，並發出逾萬張告票。警方指流動攝錄隊有助減少前線警員，與司機摩擦<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳警區行動主任總督察卓月精：「我們認為流動拍攝隊有相當正面成果，因為我們看到，路面較之前有改善，亦都有阻嚇作用，甚至教育作用。因為你沒有即時被票控，不代表你沒有被票控。較後的時間，如果你曾違例停泊的話，都有機會受票控。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424742&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbdXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=068055c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424742&h=6b06461f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424742</a>"},{"pid":"75d9f5a1c7fbca69582a3746bed161605169acbb","tid":2456495,"uid":58630,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"卓越精<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e42b1dcbe308d678f0d9e05c4ecbad3e7ab3190","tid":2456495,"uid":5502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"肯定會係咁影d靚女"},{"pid":"70e34cad574e8f07848bdf09f3c50a6fd0d841b9","tid":2456495,"uid":40272,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:58:07.000Z","msg":"影完 啲司機唔知  點趕到車？<br />\n比你影撚左老閪都泊多陣"},{"pid":"52f275613a4137a693d83fcdad7dc1fe6c377d6c","tid":2456495,"uid":34553,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"屌原來係手動影<br />\n唔怪得咁慢<br />\n有日返工喺西消防街呢架狗車行得勁慢阻住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/